 packaging made from 100% post-consumer recycled content (PCR), Loopha\u0026#39;s Hand + Body Wash is formulated with hydration-boosting glycerin and jojoba esters, which soften skin and minimize transepidermal water loss, per the brand. As for its foaming ingredients, Loopha\u0026#39;s body washes contain 3% sodium cocoyl apple amino acids (a cleansing surfactant using the amino acids from apple juice) and 3% Babassuamidopropyl Hydroxysultaine (derived from Babassu oil for dense foam).\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eLooking ahead, Loopha will expand its product offering within its current fragrance library (all created with Deciem\u0026#39;s late founder \u003ca href=\"https://fashionista.com/tag/brandon-truaxe\"\u003eBrandon Truaxe\u003c/a\u003e), adding a powder-to-foam version of its Hand + Body Wash and a Hair + Body Mist.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026#34;We like to say that we\u0026#39;re starting at \u0026#39;your sink and shower,\u0026#39; but that\u0026#39;s really just the beginning,\u0026#34; Kilner says. \u0026#34;We have 10 products launching this year, with another 30 in development right now. [The goal is to make them] practically playful and universally useful: powder formats, mists, dissolvables and much more. Our fragrance range will also expand.\u0026#34;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWith its first round of products arriving Sept. 26, Loopha will be available to shop exclusively at \u003ca href=\"https://loopha.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eloopha.com\u003c/a\u003e. Get a first look at Loopha\u0026#39;s fall body-care launches below.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cphoenix-flat-gallery id=\"ci02e7f25e40002696\" config=\"{\u0026#34;items\u0026#34;:[{\u0026#34;id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;ci02e858f500002696\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;slug\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;loopha-hand-body-wash-broadleaf-forest\u0026#34;},{\u0026#34;id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;ci02e858f9700024a9\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;slug\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;loop